### Home
GET http://localhost:3333

### Health
GET http://localhost:3333/api/health

### Metadata
GET http://localhost:3333/api/metadata

### Full database
GET http://localhost:3333/api/database

### Reload JSON without restarting server
POST http://localhost:3333/api/database/reload

### Teams
GET http://localhost:3333/api/teams

### Teams with local image URLs
GET http://localhost:3333/api/teams?assets=true

### Teams by group
GET http://localhost:3333/api/teams?group=A&assets=true

### Team by id
GET http://localhost:3333/api/teams/brazil?assets=true

### Team by slug
GET http://localhost:3333/api/teams/slug/brazil?assets=true

### Team by code
GET http://localhost:3333/api/teams/code/BRA?assets=true

### Team players
GET http://localhost:3333/api/teams/brazil/players

### Team matches
GET http://localhost:3333/api/teams/brazil/matches

### Groups
GET http://localhost:3333/api/groups

### Group with teams and matches
GET http://localhost:3333/api/groups/A

### Group teams
GET http://localhost:3333/api/groups/A/teams

### Group matches
GET http://localhost:3333/api/groups/A/matches

### Stadiums
GET http://localhost:3333/api/stadiums

### Stadium by id
GET http://localhost:3333/api/stadiums/azteca

### Matches
GET http://localhost:3333/api/matches

### Matches hydrated
GET http://localhost:3333/api/matches?hydrate=true

### Matches by group
GET http://localhost:3333/api/matches?group=A

### Matches by date
GET http://localhost:3333/api/matches?date=2026-06-13

### Matches by team
GET http://localhost:3333/api/matches/team/brazil

### Matches by code
GET http://localhost:3333/api/matches/code/BRA

### Assets
GET http://localhost:3333/api/assets

### Assets by team
GET http://localhost:3333/api/assets/team/brazil

### Assets by code
GET http://localhost:3333/api/assets/code/BRA

### Search
GET http://localhost:3333/api/search?q=brazil

### Live - jogos de hoje com placares em tempo real (OpenAI)
GET http://localhost:3333/api/live/matches

### Live - jogos de uma data especifica
GET http://localhost:3333/api/live/matches?date=2026-06-11

### Live - classificacao de todos os grupos
GET http://localhost:3333/api/live/standings

### Live - classificacao do Grupo C
GET http://localhost:3333/api/live/standings/C

### Live - estatisticas detalhadas de uma partida
GET http://localhost:3333/api/live/match/match-001/stats

### Mata-mata - chaveamento completo (atualizado por IA quando a fase comecar)
GET http://localhost:3333/api/knockout

### Mata-mata - fase atual do torneio
GET http://localhost:3333/api/knockout/phase

### Elenco oficial atualizado de uma seleção (id, slug ou código FIFA)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/live/team/brazil/squad

### Escalações oficiais de um jogo (id ou matchNumber)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/live/match/1/lineups

### Artilharia do torneio em tempo real
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/live/scorers?limit=10
